f the day and my tummy wasn't feeling so hot earlier, so I thought I'd take it easy, so I can have a pleasant rest of the night.  The service was okay and nothing over the top or spectacular.  Staff was attentive enough.  I may visit one of the CG's here in L.A./O.C. At least I know what goodness awaits me.
